/.lostpixel/current
/.lostpixel/difference

# ── Local-only working notes — never commit ─────────────────────────
# STATE.md is a per-session scratchpad Claude uses to track multi-step
# work across crashes / context wipes. Don't ship it — it's noise to
# anyone but the current operator.
STATE.md
# TODO files live locally per developer. The shared roadmap lives in
# the GitHub issue tracker / docs/ROADMAP.md. Keeping personal TODOs
# off the repo also closes a category of accidental data leak.
TODO.md
TODO2.md
ui/TODO.md
TODO-INSTRUCTIONS.md

# Lighthouse CI generates this file at workflow runtime from
# lighthouserc.json + a freshly-minted e2e-login bearer token. Carries
# secrets (the token); never commit.
lighthouserc.runtime.json

# Discord brand-image apply state ({sourceSha, discordHash} per image),
# written by apply-discord-config.mjs. Persisted across CI runs via an
# actions/cache entry (maintain-discord.yml), not the repo -- CI can't
# push to protected main. Local runs regenerate it.
.github/discord/.image-state.json

# Turborepo
.turbo
